Sentencas: Nanocrystalline Ba0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3 (BSCF-6482) powder is synthesized by combustion synthesis technique.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Nanocrystalline Ba0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3 for application as an efficient anode in solid oxide electrolyser

Sentencas: Powder calcined at 1000 degrees C reveals phase pure cubic perovskite.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Nanocrystalline Ba0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3 for application as an efficient anode in solid oxide electrolyser

Sentencas: Transmission electron microscopic (TEM) analysis exhibits soft agglomerates of average size similar to 50 nm wherein interplanar spacing for (110) and (221) resembles to the cubic lattice.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Nanocrystalline Ba0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3 for application as an efficient anode in solid oxide electrolyser

Sentencas: While DC electrical conductivity of 23 S cm(-1)@800 degrees C is observed, interfacial polarization measured by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy is found to be the least 850 degrees C (0.18 Omega cm(2)).
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Nanocrystalline Ba0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3 for application as an efficient anode in solid oxide electrolyser

Sentencas: Cell performance has been compared among BSCF-6482, BSCF-5582 and LSCF-6482 mixed ionic and electronic conducting (MIEC) and conventional electrode (LSM).
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Nanocrystalline Ba0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3 for application as an efficient anode in solid oxide electrolyser

Sentencas: Higher performance (1.37 A/cm(2)@1.3 V,800 degrees C) with high hydrogen generation rate (0.57 Nl/cm(2)/h) is found during steam electrolysis with cell fabricated using BSCF-6482 having minimal area specific resistance 0.33 Omega cm(2).
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Nanocrystalline Ba0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3 for application as an efficient anode in solid oxide electrolyser

Sentencas: Under similar operating condition, BSCF-5582, LSCF-6482 and LSM exhibit hydrogen generation rate of 0.35, 0.28 and 0.23 Nl/cm(2)/h respectively.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Nanocrystalline Ba0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3 for application as an efficient anode in solid oxide electrolyser

Sentencas: Cell microstructure is clinically correlated with the higher reactivity of BSCF-6482 air electrode in steam electrolysis.
Titulo: Synthesis and characterization of Nanocrystalline Ba0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3 for application as an efficient anode in solid oxide electrolyser
